msgid ""
"This margin is useful for when the SpringArm has a :ref:`Camera "
"<class_Camera>` as a child node: without the margin, the :ref:`Camera "
"<class_Camera>` would be placed on the exact point of collision, while "
"with the margin the :ref:`Camera <class_Camera>` would be placed close to"
" the point of collision."
